ygData.messageBody:
Well, I finally made it to level 12. Woo hhooo.

I casted whirl on myself and it hardly lasted at all. Only like 2 seconds
or something. It was late by that time
so I didn't experiment any more. Tonite I'm off to get me some pet
animation spells

Does anyone have an estimate of how long it takes in real time to get to
high hold (right?), from qeynos?

Azboklin the enchanter who FINALLY has bind and charm and hopefull won't be
made into wisp dust.
